com.magknight.route.proc.legs.parser

Class ParserHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.magknight.route.proc.legs.parser.ParserHelper

  • public class ParserHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to help parse the data provided by the X-Plane CIFP database. Pass it data in the constructor and call the methods to get a specific data field from the data passed. More information available in the ARINC database documentation. X-Plane CIFP documentation:
    Since:
    5/19/2020
    Author:
    Omar Alam and Cian Mc Sweeney.
    See Also:
    Navdata in X-Plane 11/

      • ParserHelper

        public ParserHelper(java.lang.String[] dataIn)
        Use this constructor to pass in an array containing the segments split by a comma delimeter. A deep copy of the array passed is made in this case.
        Parameters:
        dataIn - The array with the data segments.
